# 🏡 Bengaluru Property Price Intelligence (Excel Project)

## 📊 Project Overview

This project analyzes real estate property data from Bengaluru to help users understand pricing trends, locality comparisons, and property configurations. The dashboard is designed for non-technical users to explore property insights interactively.

---

## 🔧 Tools Used

* Microsoft Excel
* Power Query (Data Cleaning)
* Pivot Tables
* Data Visualization

---

## 🧹 Data Cleaning

* Cleaned raw housing data using Power Query
* Extracted BHK values from text fields
* Converted price formats (Cr/Lakh to numeric Lakhs)
* Standardized locality and area values

---

## 📈 Feature Engineering

* Created **Price per Sq Ft** metric:

  Price_per_sqft = (Price in Lakhs × 100000) / Area

---

## 📊 Analysis Performed

* BHK-wise price and area analysis
* Locality-wise price comparison
* Identification of high-value and low-value areas
* Property distribution insights

---

## 📊 Dashboard Features

* KPI Cards (Avg Price, Avg Area, Price per Sqft, Listings)
* Top Localities by Price per Sqft
* BHK Distribution Analysis
* Buyer Comparison Tool (interactive filtering)

---

